subTitle: Comprehensive coverage of events in Japan and Asia. It explains the day's developments and what is behind them.

title: Direct Talk
subTitle: Nagasaka Mago discusses his work, creating art from e-waste collected in Ghanaian slums, using much of the proceeds to benefit the community, and shares his vision for an influential process.
